OBJECT Report 16472 Old Form ST-3
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=24-04-16;
    Time=12:00:00 PM;
    Version List=NAVIN9.00.00.45778;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=[ENU=Old Form ST-3;
               ENN=Old Form ST-3];
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  CompInfo.GET;
                  IF STN = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16500);
                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::" " THEN
                    ERROR(Text16501);
                  IF Year = 0 THEN
                    ERROR(Text16502);
                  IF FooterPlace = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text16503);
                  IF FooterDate = 0D THEN
                    ERROR(Text16504);
                  IPserviceDistributor := FALSE;
                  Location1.RESET;
                  Location1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                  Location1.SETRANGE("Input Service Distributor",TRUE);
                  IF Location1.FINDFIRST THEN
                    IPserviceDistributor := TRUE;

                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly THEN BEGIN
                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                      Month[1] := 'Apr';
                      Month[2] := 'May';
                      Month[3] := 'June';
                      Month[4] := 'July';
                      Month[5] := 'Aug';
                      Month[6] := 'Sept';
                    END ELSE
                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                        Month[1] := 'Oct';
                        Month[2] := 'Nov';
                        Month[3] := 'Dec';
                        Month[4] := 'Jan';
                        Month[5] := 'Feb';
                        Month[6] := 'March';
                      END;
                  END;
                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly THEN BEGIN
                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                      Quarter[1] := 'Apr-June';
                      Quarter[2] := 'July-Sept'
                    END ELSE
                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                        Quarter[3] := 'Oct-Dec';
                        Quarter[4] := 'Jan-March';
                      END;
                  END;
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 5444;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  SelectMonthRange1 := '';
                                  SelectMonthRange2 := '';
                                  CLEAR(ConstitutionOfAssessee);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    SelectMonthRange1 := 'a'
                                  ELSE
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      SelectMonthRange2 := 'a';
                                  IF CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" THEN
                                    LTU := 'Y'
                                  ELSE
                                    LTU := 'N';
                                  IF STRegistrationNo.GET(STN) THEN;
                                  IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::"Public Limited Co." THEN
                                    ConstitutionOfAssessee[3] := 'a'
                                  ELSE
                                    IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::"Private Limited Co." THEN
                                      ConstitutionOfAssessee[4] := 'a'
                                    ELSE
                                      IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::Others THEN
                                        ConstitutionOfAssessee[7] := 'a'
                                      ELSE
                                        IF (CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::Others) OR
                                           (CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::Government)
                                        THEN
                                          ConstitutionOfAssessee[7] := 'a'
                                        ELSE
                                          IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::"Individual/Proprietary" THEN
                                            ConstitutionOfAssessee[1] := 'a'
                                          ELSE
                                            IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::"Registered Trust" THEN
                                              ConstitutionOfAssessee[5] := 'a'
                                            ELSE
                                              IF CompInfo."Company Status" = CompInfo."Company Status"::Partnership THEN
                                                ConstitutionOfAssessee[6] := 'a'
                                              ELSE
                                                ConstitutionOfAssessee[2] := 'a';
                                  FinancialYear := FORMAT(Year) + '-' + COPYSTR(FORMAT(Year + 1),3,2);

                                  STGroupRegistration.RESET;
                                  STGroupRegistration.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF STGroupRegistration.FINDFIRST OR CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" OR IfvalueComputed THEN
                                    SectionPrinted := FALSE;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 3569;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16592;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Service Tax Registration No.,Service Tax Group);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CLEAR(AmtAgainstServiceprovided);
                                  CLEAR(AdvanceAmtForService);
                                  CLEAR(AmtAgainstExportService);
                                  CLEAR(AmtAgainstExemptedService);
                                  CLEAR(AmtAgainstPureAgent);
                                  CLEAR(AmatementAmt);
                                  CLEAR(GrossTaxableAmt);
                                  CLEAR(TaxableAgainstExemptedService);
                                  CLEAR(TaxableAmtAgainstPureAgent);
                                  CLEAR(TaxableAmatementAmt);
                                  CLEAR(TaxableAmtAgainstExportService);
                                  CLEAR(STPayable);
                                  CLEAR(AbatmentNotificationCount);

                                  ServiceProvider := '';
                                  ServiceReciever := '';

                                  IF "Liable to pay Service Tax as" = "Liable to pay Service Tax as"::"Service Provider" THEN
                                    ServiceProvider := 'a'
                                  ELSE
                                    ServiceReciever := 'a';

                                  IF STGroup.GET("Service Tax Group") THEN;
                                  ServiceNotificationNo.RESET;
                                  ServiceNotificationNo.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group","Service Tax Group");
                                  ServiceNotificationNo.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.","Service Tax Registration No.");
                                  ServiceNotificationNo.SETRANGE(Type,ServiceNotificationNo.Type::Exemption);
                                  ServiceNotificationNo.SETFILTER("Notification No.",'<>%1','');
                                  IF ServiceNotificationNo.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    NotificationAvailed := 'Y'
                                  ELSE
                                    NotificationAvailed := 'N';
                                END;
                                 }

               SourceExpr=Assessee_7_CAP_Ctr1500007Lbl }

    { 1500009;1;Column  ;i___a_service_provider__orCaption;

    { 7887;1   ;DataItem;Integer6            ;

                                 ORDER(Ascending)

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  ServiceNotificationNo1.RESET;
                                  ServiceNotificationNo1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1170000020;2;Column;Integer6_Number    ;

    { 7365;1   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16593;

                                       Notification No.=FILTER(<>''));
               DataItemLink=Service Tax Group=FIELD(Service Tax Group),
                            Service Tax Registration No.=FIELD(Service Tax Registration No.) }

    { 1500035;2;Column  ;Service_Notification_No___Notification_No__;

    { 2800;1   ;DataItem;<Service Notification SI No.>;

                            Service Tax Registration No.=FIELD(Service Tax Registration No.) }

    { 8897;1   ;DataItem;Integer10           ;

    { 1170000028;2;Column;Integer10_Number   ;

    { 1501808;2;Column  ;If_Ctr1501808       ;

    { 1501809;2;Column  ;DCaption_Ctr1501809 ;
               SourceExpr=DCaption_Ctr1501809Lbl }

    { 5104;1   ;DataItem;Integer1            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  k@1500000 : Integer;
                                BEGIN
                                  IfvalueComputed := TRUE;

                                  IF CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" THEN
                                    IfvalueComputed := FALSE
                                  ELSE
                                    IF IPserviceDistributor THEN
                                      IfvalueComputed := FALSE;

                                  k := 0;
                                  IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                    STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Group");

                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                    IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        k := 0;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 1;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 2;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 3;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 4;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 5;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                            OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          k := 6;

                                        IF k > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          IF (NOT STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment") AND ((STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase) AND
                                                                                                     STEntryDetail."Reverse Charge" AND (ServiceReciever <> ''))
                                          THEN
                                            AmtAgainstServiceprovided[k] += STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                          IF (NOT STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment") AND ((STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                                                                                     (ServiceProvider <> ''))
                                          THEN
                                            AmtAgainstServiceprovided[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                          IF STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment" AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                             (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                          THEN
                                            AdvanceAmtForService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" = 0) AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale)
                                             AND (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                          THEN BEGIN
                                            IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::Export) AND
                                               NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent"
                                            THEN
                                              AmtAgainstExportService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount"
                                            ELSE
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::Exempted) AND
                                                 NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent"
                                              THEN
                                                AmtAgainstExemptedService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount"
                                              ELSE
                                                IF STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent" THEN
                                                  AmtAgainstPureAgent[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";
                                          END;
                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::" ") AND
                                             (NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent") AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                             (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                          THEN
                                            AmatementAmt[k] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax Abatement %" * -STEntryDetail."Base Amount" / 100;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                    IF ServiceProvider <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                      k := 0;
                                      STEntry.RESET;
                                      STEntry.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Registration No.");
                                      STEntry.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Group");
                                      STEntry.SETRANGE(Type,STEntry.Type::Sale);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STEntry.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          k := 0;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 1;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 2;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 3;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 4;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 5;
                                          IF ((STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                              OR (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 6;
                                          IF k > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            GrossTaxableAmt[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount";
                                            IF STEntry."Service Tax Amount" = 0 THEN BEGIN
                                              IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::Export) AND
                                                 NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent"
                                              THEN
                                                TaxableAmtAgainstExportService[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount"
                                              ELSE
                                                IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::Exempted) AND
                                                   NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent"
                                                THEN
                                                  TaxableAgainstExemptedService[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount"
                                                ELSE
                                                  IF STEntry."ST Pure Agent" THEN
                                                    TaxableAmtAgainstPureAgent[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount";
                                            END;
                                            IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::" ") AND
                                               (NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent")
                                            THEN
                                              TaxableAmatementAmt[k] += STEntry."Service Tax Abatement" * -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount" / 100;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STEntry.NEXT = 0);
                                    END;
                                  END
                                  ELSE
                                    IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                      STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                      STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Group");

                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          k := 0;
                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 1;
                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 2;
                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 3;
                                          IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                          THEN
                                            k := 4;

                                          IF k > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            IF (NOT STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment") AND ((STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase) AND
                                                                                                       STEntryDetail."Reverse Charge" AND (ServiceReciever <> ''))
                                            THEN
                                              AmtAgainstServiceprovided[k] += STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                            IF (NOT STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment") AND ((STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                                                                                       (ServiceProvider <> ''))
                                            THEN
                                              AmtAgainstServiceprovided[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                            IF STEntryDetail."Serv. Tax on Advance Payment" AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                               (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                            THEN
                                              AdvanceAmtForService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";

                                            IF (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" = 0) AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale)
                                               AND (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::Export) AND
                                                 NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent"
                                              THEN
                                                AmtAgainstExportService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount"
                                              ELSE
                                                IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::Exempted) AND
                                                   NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent"
                                                THEN
                                                  AmtAgainstExemptedService[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount"
                                                ELSE
                                                  IF STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent" THEN
                                                    AmtAgainstPureAgent[k] += -STEntryDetail."Base Amount";
                                            END;
                                            IF (STEntryDetail."Nature of Services" = STEntryDetail."Nature of Services"::" ") AND
                                               (NOT STEntryDetail."ST Pure Agent") AND (STEntryDetail.Type = STEntryDetail.Type::Sale) AND
                                               (ServiceProvider <> '')
                                            THEN
                                              AmatementAmt[k] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax Abatement %" * -STEntryDetail."Base Amount" / 100;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                      IF ServiceProvider <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                        k := 0;
                                        STEntry.RESET;
                                        STEntry.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Registration No.");
                                        STEntry.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code","ST Group/ST Registration No."."Service Tax Group");
                                        STEntry.SETRANGE(Type,STEntry.Type::Sale);
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                          STEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                          STEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                        IF STEntry.FIND('-') THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            k := 0;
                                            IF (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                            THEN
                                              k := 1;
                                            IF (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                            THEN
                                              k := 2;
                                            IF (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                            THEN
                                              k := 3;
                                            IF (STEntry."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND (STEntry."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                            THEN
                                              k := 4;
                                            IF k > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                              GrossTaxableAmt[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount";
                                              IF STEntry."Service Tax Amount" = 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::Export) AND
                                                   NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent"
                                                THEN
                                                  TaxableAmtAgainstExportService[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount"
                                                ELSE
                                                  IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::Exempted) AND
                                                     NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent"
                                                  THEN
                                                    TaxableAgainstExemptedService[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount"
                                                  ELSE
                                                    IF STEntry."ST Pure Agent" THEN
                                                      TaxableAmtAgainstPureAgent[k] += -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount";
                                              END;
                                              IF (STEntry."Nature of Services" = STEntry."Nature of Services"::" ") AND
                                                 (NOT STEntry."ST Pure Agent")
                                              THEN
                                                TaxableAmatementAmt[k] += STEntry."Service Tax Abatement" * -STEntry."Service Tax Base Amount" / 100;
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (STEntry.NEXT = 0);
                                      END;
                                    END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1501654;2;Column  ;N_                  ;
               SourceExpr='N' }

    { 1500333;2;Column  ;AdvanceAmtForService_3__;

               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExportService[2]) }

    { 1500339;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExportService_3__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExportService[3]) }

    { 1500340;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExportService_4__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExportService[4]) }

               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExportService[5]) }

    { 1500343;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExemptedService_1__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExemptedService[1]) }

    { 1500344;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExemptedService_2__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExemptedService[2]) }

    { 1500345;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExemptedService_3__;

    { 1500346;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExemptedService_4__;

    { 1500347;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstExemptedService_5__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstExemptedService[5]) }

    { 1500349;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstPureAgent_1__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstPureAgent[1]) }

    { 1500350;2;Column  ;AmtAgainstPureAgent_2__;
               SourceExpr=(AmtAgainstPureAgent[2]) }

               SourceExpr=V5__CAP_Ctr1501199Lbl }

    { 1501200;2;Column  ;V1_CAP_Ctr1501200   ;
               SourceExpr=V1_CAP_Ctr1501200Lbl }

    { 8373;2   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16474;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Service Tax Registration No.,Service Tax Group Code,Type,ST Pure Agent,Nature of Services,Service Tax %)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Type=FILTER(Sale|Purchase),
                                       ST Pure Agent=FILTER(No),
                                       Nature of Services=FILTER(' '));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CLEAR(STBase);
                               CLEAR(STPayable);
                               CLEAR(STeCessPayable);
                               CLEAR(STSHECessPayable);

                               IF CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK
                                 ;
                               IF IPserviceDistributor THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               PercentText := '';
                               IF Integer7.Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                 SETRANGE("Service Tax %",5);
                                 PercentText := '(i)  Value on which service tax is payable @ 5%';
                               END;
                               IF Integer7.Number = 2 THEN BEGIN
                                 SETRANGE("Service Tax %",8);
                                 PercentText := '8';
                                 PercentText := '(ii)  Value on which service tax is payable @ 8%';
                               END;
                               IF Integer7.Number = 3 THEN BEGIN
                                 SETRANGE("Service Tax %",10);
                                 PercentText := '(iii)  Value on which service tax is payable @ 10%';
                               END;
                               IF Integer7.Number = 4 THEN BEGIN
                                 SETRANGE("Service Tax %",12);
                                 PercentText := '(iv)  Value on which service tax is payable @ 12%';
                               END;
                               IF Integer7.Number = 5 THEN BEGIN
                                 SETFILTER("Service Tax %",'<>5&<>8&<>10&<>12');
                                 PercentText := '(v)  Other Rate if any (applicable)' ;
                               END;

                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(STBase[1],STBase[2],STPayable[1],STPayable[2],STeCessPayable[1],STeCessPayable[2],
                                 STSHECessPayable[1],STSHECessPayable[2]);
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(STBase[3],STBase[4],STPayable[3],STPayable[4],STeCessPayable[3],STeCessPayable[4],
                                 STSHECessPayable[3],STSHECessPayable[4]);
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(STBase[5],STBase[6],STPayable[5],STPayable[6],STeCessPayable[5],STeCessPayable[6],
                                 STSHECessPayable[5],STSHECessPayable[6]);

                               IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                               ELSE
                                 IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                   SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1));

                               j := 0;
                               IfPrinted := FALSE;

                               IF FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                 REPEAT
                                   IF (((Type =  Type::Sale) AND (ServiceProvider <> '')) OR ((Type = Type::Purchase) AND
                                    "Reverse Charge" AND ((ServiceReciever <> ''))))
                                   THEN
                                     MARK(TRUE);
                                 UNTIL NEXT = 0;
                                 MARKEDONLY(TRUE);
                                 IF COUNT > 0 THEN
                                   FINDFIRST;
                               END
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Integer7.Number = 5 THEN
                                    PercentText := '(v)  Other Rate if any (applicable) @ ' + FORMAT("Service Tax %") + FORMAT(' %');

                                  j := 0;

                                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly THEN BEGIN
                                    IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                        OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                    THEN BEGIN
                                      j := 1;
                                    END ELSE
                                      IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                          OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                      THEN BEGIN
                                        j := 2;
                                      END ELSE
                                        IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                            OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN BEGIN
                                          j := 3;
                                        END ELSE
                                          IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                              OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                          THEN BEGIN
                                            j := 4;
                                          END ELSE
                                            IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                                OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              j := 5;
                                            END ELSE
                                              IF (("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                                  OR ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                              THEN
                                                j := 6;
                                  END;

                                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                      j := 1
                                    ELSE
                                      IF ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                        j := 2
                                      ELSE
                                        IF ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                          j := 3
                                        ELSE
                                          IF ("Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND ("Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) THEN
                                            j := 4;
                                  END;

                                  IF j > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    IF (Type = Type::Sale) AND (ServiceProvider <> '') THEN BEGIN
                                      STBase[j] := -"Base Amount" * (100 - "Service Tax Abatement %") / 100;
                                      STPayable[j] := (-"Base Amount" * (100 - "Service Tax Abatement %") / 100) * "Service Tax %" / 100;
                                      TotalSTPayable := STPayable[j];
                                    END
                                    ELSE BEGIN
                                      STBase[j] := "Base Amount" * (100 - "Service Tax Abatement %") / 100;
                                      STPayable[j] := ("Base Amount" * (100 - "Service Tax Abatement %") / 100) * "Service Tax %" / 100;
                                      TotalSTPayable := STPayable[j];
                                    END;
                                    STeCessPayable[j] := STPayable[j] * "Service Tax eCess %" / 100;
                                    STSHECessPayable[j] := STPayable[j] * "Service Tax SHE Cess %" / 100;
                                    TotalSTeCessPayable := STeCessPayable[j];
                                    TotalSTSHECessPayable := STSHECessPayable[j];
                                  END;

                                  IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly) OR
                                     (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly)
                                  THEN
                                    IfPrinted := TRUE;
                                END;

               DataItemLinkReference=ST Group/ST Registration No.;
               DataItemLink=Service Tax Registration No.=FIELD(Service Tax Registration No.),
                            Service Tax Group Code=FIELD(Service Tax Group) }

    { 1500244;3;Column  ;STBase_4__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[4]) }

    { 1500245;3;Column  ;STBase_5__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[5]) }

    { 1500246;3;Column  ;STBase_2__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[2]) }

    { 1500247;3;Column  ;STBase_1__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[1]) }

    { 1500269;3;Column  ;STBase_3__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[3]) }

    { 1500413;3;Column  ;STBase_6__          ;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[6]) }

    { 1500416;3;Column  ;PercentText         ;
               SourceExpr=PercentText }

    { 1500950;3;Column  ;IPserviceDistributor;
               SourceExpr=IPserviceDistributor }

    { 1500951;3;Column  ;CompInfo__Input_Service_Distributor_;
               SourceExpr=CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" }

    { 1500419;3;Column  ;STBase_4___Ctr1500419;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[4]) }

    { 1500420;3;Column  ;STBase_3___Ctr1500420;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[3]) }

    { 1500421;3;Column  ;STBase_2___Ctr1500421;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[2]) }

    { 1500422;3;Column  ;STBase_1___Ctr1500422;
               SourceExpr=(STBase[1]) }

    { 1500438;3;Column  ;PercentText_Ctr1500438;
               SourceExpr=PercentText }

    { 1170000030;3;Column;Service_Tax_Entry_Details_Entry_No_;
               SourceExpr="Entry No." }

    { 1170000031;3;Column;Service_Tax_Entry_Details_Service_Tax__;
               SourceExpr="Service Tax %" }

    { 1170000032;3;Column;Service_Tax_Entry_Details_Service_Tax_Registration_No_;
               SourceExpr="Service Tax Registration No." }

    { 1170000033;3;Column;Service_Tax_Entry_Details_Service_Tax_Group_Code;
               SourceExpr="Service Tax Group Code" }

    { 8813;2   ;DataItem;Integer8            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(>0));
               MaxIteration=1;
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  I@1500000 : Integer;
                                BEGIN
                                  FOR I := 1 TO 6 DO BEGIN
                                    STPayable[I] := 0;
                                    STeCessPayable[I] := 0;
                                    STSHECessPayable[I] := 0;
                                    GrossTaxableAmt[I] := 0;
                                    TaxableAmtAgainstExportService[I] := 0;
                                    TaxableAgainstExemptedService[I] := 0;
                                    TaxableAmtAgainstPureAgent[I] := 0;
                                    TaxableAmatementAmt[I] := 0;
                                  END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500969;3;Column  ;PercentText_Ctr1500969;
               SourceExpr=PercentText }

    { 1500949;3;Column  ;IfPrinted           ;
               SourceExpr=IfPrinted }

    { 1170000034;3;Column;Integer8_Number    ;
               SourceExpr=Number }

    { 4152;    ;DataItem;Integer2            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CLEAR(STPaidinCash);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  STReturnPeriod@1500000 : Record 16588;
                                  STPeriodDueDates@1500001 : Record 16589;
                                  ReturnFilingDate@1500002 : Date;
                                  PrevReturnFilingDate@1500003 : Date;
                                  PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate@1500004 : Date;
                                  STMonthlyPaymentDetail@1500005 : Record 16591;
                                  PrevDocNo@1500006 : Code[20];
                                  K@1500007 : Integer;
                                  IsArrear@1500008 : Boolean;
                                  PaymentDueDate@1500009 : Date;
                                BEGIN
                                  IfvalueComputed := TRUE;

                                  IF CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" THEN
                                    IfvalueComputed := FALSE
                                  ELSE
                                    IF IPserviceDistributor THEN
                                      IfvalueComputed := FALSE;

                                  IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                    STReturnPeriod.GET(Year,MonthRange);
                                    STReturnPeriod.TESTFIELD("Return Filing Due Date");
                                    ReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Return Filing Due Date";
                                    IF STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
                                      IF ReturnFilingDate > STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" THEN
                                        ReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date";
                                    END;

                                    // Prev Return period
                                    STReturnPeriod.RESET;
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                      STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE(Year,Year - 1);
                                      STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE("Return Period",STReturnPeriod."Return Period"::"Oct-Mar");
                                    END;
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                      STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE(Year,Year);
                                      STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Apr-Sep");
                                    END;
                                    STReturnPeriod.FINDFIRST;
                                    PrevReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Return Filing Due Date";
                                    IF STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
                                      IF PrevReturnFilingDate > STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" THEN
                                        PrevReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date";
                                    END;

                                    STPeriodDueDates.RESET;
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE(Year,Year - 1);
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Oct-Mar");
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("ST Payment Period",STPeriodDueDates."ST Payment Period"::Monthly);
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Month/Qtr",3);
                                    END;
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE(Year,Year);
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Apr-Sep");
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("ST Payment Period",STPeriodDueDates."ST Payment Period"::Monthly);
                                      STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Month/Qtr",9);
                                    END;
                                    STPeriodDueDates.FINDFIRST;
                                    STPeriodDueDates.TESTFIELD("Payment Due Date");
                                    PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate := STPeriodDueDates."Payment Due Date" ;

                                    // First cater first month
                                    PrevDocNo := '';
                                    STPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                    STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate + 1,PrevReturnFilingDate);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate + 1,PrevReturnFilingDate);
                                    STPaymentDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Group Code",'<>%1','');
                                    IF STPaymentDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STPaidinCash[1] := STPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                              STPaidinCredit[1] := STPaidinCredit[1] + (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Reverse Charge PAYMENT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STPaidinCash[1] := STPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                              STPaidinCredit[1] := STPaidinCredit[1] + (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // ECess
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No. (eCess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STeCessPaidinCash[1] := STeCessPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                              STeCessPaidinCredit[1] := STeCessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Reverse Charge Ecess PAYMENT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No. (eCESS)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STeCessPaidinCash[1] := STeCessPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                              STeCessPaidinCredit[1] := STeCessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                (STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // SHECess
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Doc. No. (SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                              STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Reverse Charge SHE Cess PAYMENT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No.(SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                              STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Other payments
                                        IF PrevDocNo <> STPaymentDetail."Document No." THEN BEGIN
                                          PrevDocNo := STPaymentDetail."Document No.";
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          IF STMonthlyPaymentDetail.FIND('-') THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCash[1] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[1] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other eCess Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[1] :=
                                                  STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other SHE Cess Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmtInterestPaid[1] := STOtherAmtInterestPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Interest Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[1] := STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Penalty Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[1] := STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Section 73 A Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtOtherPaid[1] := STOtherAmtOtherPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Any Other Amount";
                                                InsertChallanDetail(0,STPaymentDetail."Challan No.",STPaymentDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STMonthlyPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL STPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                    // Other months
                                    PrevDocNo := '';
                                    STPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                    STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevReturnFilingDate + 1,ReturnFilingDate);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevReturnFilingDate + 1,ReturnFilingDate);
                                    STPaymentDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Group Code",'<>%1','');
                                    IF STPaymentDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            K := 0;
                                            PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                            IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 6;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 1;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 2;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 3;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 4;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 5;
                                            IF (((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                 (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 6;

                                            IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                              STPaidinCash[K] := STPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                              STPaidinCredit[K] := STPaidinCredit[K] + (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                            END;
                                            IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                              STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                              STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Reverse Charge PAYMENT
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
