                                              STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                              InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                        // Other payments
                                        IF PrevDocNo <> STPaymentDetail."Document No." THEN BEGIN
                                          PrevDocNo := STPaymentDetail."Document No.";
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          IF STMonthlyPaymentDetail.FIND('-') THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 6;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1) AND
                                                   (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 5;
                                              IF (((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept")) OR
                                                  ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                   (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March")))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 6;
                                              IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other eCess Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] :=
                                                  STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other SHE Cess Arrear Amt";
                                                STOtherAmtInterestPaid[K] := STOtherAmtInterestPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Interest Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[K] := STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Penalty Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[K] := STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Section 73 A Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtOtherPaid[K] := STOtherAmtOtherPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Any Other Amount";
                                                InsertChallanDetail(0,STPaymentDetail."Challan No.",STPaymentDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STMonthlyPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL STPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                  END ELSE
                                    IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                      STReturnPeriod.GET(Year,MonthRange);
                                      STReturnPeriod.TESTFIELD("Return Filing Due Date");
                                      ReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Return Filing Due Date";
                                      IF STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ReturnFilingDate > STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" THEN
                                          ReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date";
                                      END;

                                      // Prev Return period
                                      STReturnPeriod.RESET;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                        STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE(Year,Year - 1);
                                        STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE("Return Period",STReturnPeriod."Return Period"::"Oct-Mar");
                                      END;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                        STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE(Year,Year);
                                        STReturnPeriod.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Apr-Sep");
                                      END;
                                      STReturnPeriod.FINDFIRST;
                                      PrevReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Return Filing Due Date";
                                      IF STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" <> 0D THEN BEGIN
                                        IF PrevReturnFilingDate > STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date" THEN
                                          PrevReturnFilingDate := STReturnPeriod."Actual Return Filed Date";
                                      END;

                                      STPeriodDueDates.RESET;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE(Year,Year - 1);
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Oct-Mar");
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("ST Payment Period",STPeriodDueDates."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly);
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Month/Qtr",4);
                                      END;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE(Year,Year);
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Return Period",STPeriodDueDates."Return Period"::"Apr-Sep");
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("ST Payment Period",STPeriodDueDates."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly);
                                        STPeriodDueDates.SETRANGE("Month/Qtr",2);
                                      END;
                                      STPeriodDueDates.FINDFIRST;
                                      STPeriodDueDates.TESTFIELD("Payment Due Date");
                                      PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate := STPeriodDueDates."Payment Due Date" ;

                                      // First cater first month of quarter
                                      PrevDocNo := '';
                                      STPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate + 1,PrevReturnFilingDate);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevPeriodLastMonthDueDate + 1,PrevReturnFilingDate);
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Group Code",'<>%1','');
                                      IF STPaymentDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[1] := STPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[1] := STPaidinCredit[1] + (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[3] := STPaidinCash[3] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[3] := STPaidinCredit[3] + (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[1] := STPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[1] := STPaidinCredit[1] + (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[3] := STPaidinCash[3] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[3] := STPaidinCredit[3] + (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // ECess
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No. (eCess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[1] := STeCessPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[1] := STeCessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[3] := STeCessPaidinCash[3] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[3] := STeCessPaidinCredit[3] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge Ecess PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No. (eCESS)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[1] := STeCessPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[1] := STeCessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[3] := STeCessPaidinCash[3] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[3] := STeCessPaidinCredit[3] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // SHECess
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Doc. No. (SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[3] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[3] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[3] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[3] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge SHE Cess PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No.(SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[1] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[1] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                              END;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[3] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[3] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[3] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[3] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Other payments
                                          IF PrevDocNo <> STPaymentDetail."Document No." THEN BEGIN
                                            PrevDocNo := STPaymentDetail."Document No.";
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                            IF STMonthlyPaymentDetail.FIND('-') THEN
                                              REPEAT
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                                THEN BEGIN
                                                  STOtherAmtPaidinCash[1] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[1] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other eCess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[1] :=
                                                    STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other SHE Cess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtInterestPaid[1] := STOtherAmtInterestPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Interest Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[1] := STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Penalty Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[1] := STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Section 73 A Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtOtherPaid[1] := STOtherAmtOtherPaid[1] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Any Other Amount";
                                                  InsertChallanDetail(0,STPaymentDetail."Challan No.",STPaymentDetail."Challan Date",1);
                                                END;
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                                THEN BEGIN
                                                  STOtherAmtPaidinCash[3] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[3] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other eCess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[3] :=
                                                    STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other SHE Cess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtInterestPaid[3] := STOtherAmtInterestPaid[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Interest Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[3] := STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Penalty Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[3] := STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Section 73 A Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtOtherPaid[3] := STOtherAmtOtherPaid[3] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Any Other Amount";
                                                  InsertChallanDetail(0,STPaymentDetail."Challan No.",STPaymentDetail."Challan Date",3);
                                                END;
                                              UNTIL STMonthlyPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL STPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                      // Other Quarters
                                      PrevDocNo := '';
                                      STPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevReturnFilingDate + 1,ReturnFilingDate);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",PrevReturnFilingDate + 1,ReturnFilingDate);
                                      STPaymentDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Group Code",'<>%1','');
                                      IF STPaymentDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[K] := STPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[K] := STPaidinCredit[K] + (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STPaidinCash[K] := STPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STPaidinCredit[K] := STPaidinCredit[K] + (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount";
                                                STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // ECess
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Document No. (eCess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[K] := STeCessPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[K] := STeCessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge Ecess PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No. (eCESS)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STeCessPaidinCash[K] := STeCessPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STeCessPaidinCredit[K] := STeCessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess";
                                                STOtherAmteCessPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount eCess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // SHECess
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Payment Doc. No. (SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Sale);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[K] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[K] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] + -STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (-STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Reverse Charge SHE Cess PAYMENT
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Rev.Ch. Pmt. Doc. No.(SHECess)",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Group Code",STPaymentDetail."Service Tax Group Code");
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              PaymentDueDate := GetPaymentDueDate(STEntryDetail."Posting Date");
                                              IsArrear := STPaymentDetail."Posting Date" > PaymentDueDate ;

                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                  (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;

                                              IF (K > 0) AND (NOT IsArrear) THEN BEGIN
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCash[K] := STSHEcessPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STSHEcessPaidinCredit[K] := STSHEcessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                              IF (K > 0) AND IsArrear THEN BEGIN
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] + STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess";
                                                STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] := STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCredit[K] +
                                                  (STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount" - STEntryDetail."Payment Amount SHE Cess");
                                                InsertChallanDetail(STEntryDetail."Entry No.",STEntryDetail."Challan No.",STEntryDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                          // Other payments
                                          IF PrevDocNo <> STPaymentDetail."Document No." THEN BEGIN
                                            PrevDocNo := STPaymentDetail."Document No.";
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.RESET;
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                            STMonthlyPaymentDetail.SETRANGE("Document No.",STPaymentDetail."Document No.");
                                            IF STMonthlyPaymentDetail.FIND('-') THEN
                                              REPEAT
                                                IF (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" < DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept") THEN
                                                  K := 2;
                                                IF (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" < DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March") THEN
                                                  K := 4;
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 1;
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 3;
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept"))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 2;
                                                IF ((STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                    (STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Liability Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) AND (MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March"))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 4;

                                                IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                  STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmtPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] := STOtherAmteCessPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other eCess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] :=
                                                    STOtherAmtSHECessPaidinCash[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Other SHE Cess Arrear Amt";
                                                  STOtherAmtInterestPaid[K] := STOtherAmtInterestPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Interest Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[K] := STOtherAmtPenaltyPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Penalty Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[K] := STOtherAmtSec73AAmtPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Section 73 A Amount";
                                                  STOtherAmtOtherPaid[K] := STOtherAmtOtherPaid[K] + STMonthlyPaymentDetail."Any Other Amount";
                                                  InsertChallanDetail(0,STPaymentDetail."Challan No.",STPaymentDetail."Challan Date",K);
                                                END;
                                              UNTIL STMonthlyPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL STPaymentDetail.NEXT = 0;
                                    END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500800;1;Column  ;STPaidinCredit_1_   ;

    { 1283;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table16595;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Document No.,Service Tax Registration No.,Service Tax Group Code,Line No.,Source Doc Line No.)
                                 WHERE(Posted=FILTER(Yes));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                               IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Source Document Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                               IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Source Document Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IfvalueComputed := TRUE;
                                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly THEN BEGIN
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                      IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) THEN
                                        "Month/Quarter" := 'April'
                                      ELSE
                                        IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) THEN
                                          "Month/Quarter" := 'May'
                                        ELSE
                                          IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                            "Month/Quarter" := 'June'
                                          ELSE
                                            IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) THEN
                                              "Month/Quarter" := 'July'
                                            ELSE
                                              IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) THEN
                                                "Month/Quarter" := 'August'
                                              ELSE
                                                IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                                  "Month/Quarter" := 'Sept';
                                    END ELSE
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)) THEN
                                          "Month/Quarter" := 'Oct'
                                        ELSE
                                          IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)) THEN
                                            "Month/Quarter" := 'Nov'
                                          ELSE
                                            IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                              "Month/Quarter" := 'Dec'
                                            ELSE
                                              IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)) THEN
                                                "Month/Quarter" := 'Jan'
                                              ELSE
                                                IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1) THEN
                                                  "Month/Quarter" := 'Feb'
                                                ELSE
                                                  IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) THEN
                                                    "Month/Quarter" := 'March';
                                      END;
                                  END;
                                  IF CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly THEN BEGIN
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                      IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                        "Month/Quarter" := 'Apr-Jun'
                                      ELSE
                                        IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                          "Month/Quarter" := 'Jul-Sept';
                                    END ELSE
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                        IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                          "Month/Quarter" := 'Oct-Dec'
                                        ELSE
                                          IF ("Source Document Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND ("Source Document Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year)) THEN
                                            "Month/Quarter" := 'Jan-Mar';
                                      END;
                                  END;
                                  SNo += 1;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1500425;1;Column  ;ST3_Source_Document_Detail__Source_Document_No__;
               SourceExpr="Source Document No." }

               SourceExpr="Source Doc Line No." }

    { 7913;    ;DataItem;Integer3            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CLEAR(CrTakenIPService);
                               CLEAR(OpeningCenvatIPCredit);
                               CLEAR(OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess);
                               CLEAR(CCSTOnInputs);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  Service_Provider@1500000 : Text[1];
                                  Service_Reciever@1500001 : Text[1];
                                  STGroup_STRegn@1500002 : Record 16592;
                                  RG23APartII@1500003 : Record 13720;
                                  Location@1500004 : Record 14;
                                  RG23CPartII@1500005 : Record 13722;
                                  STEntryDetails@1500006 : Record 16474;
                                  K@1500010 : Integer;
                                BEGIN
                                  IfvalueComputed := TRUE;
                                  // header1
                                  Service_Provider := '';
                                  Service_Reciever := '';
                                  STGroup_STRegn.RESET;
                                  STGroup_STRegn.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF STGroup_STRegn.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      IF Service_Provider = '' THEN BEGIN
                                        IF STGroup_STRegn."Liable to pay Service Tax as" = STGroup_STRegn."Liable to pay Service Tax as"::"Service Provider" THEN
                                          Service_Provider := 'a'
                                      END;
                                      IF Service_Reciever = '' THEN BEGIN
                                        IF STGroup_STRegn."Liable to pay Service Tax as" = STGroup_STRegn."Liable to pay Service Tax as"::"Service Receiver" THEN
                                          Service_Reciever := 'a'
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL STGroup_STRegn.NEXT = 0;

                                  IF (Service_Provider <> '') AND
                                     ((Service_Reciever = '') AND NOT (CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" OR IPserviceDistributor))
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ProvExemptedGoods OR ManuExemptedGoods THEN
                                      MainSeperateAcc := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      MainSeperateAcc := 'N';

                                    IF ProvExemptedGoods THEN
                                      ProvExemptedGoodsText := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      ProvExemptedGoodsText := 'N';

                                    IF ManuExemptedGoods THEN
                                      ManuExemptedGoodsText := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      ManuExemptedGoodsText := 'N';
                                  END;
                                  IF (Service_Provider <> '') AND (Service_Reciever <> '') THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ProvExemptedGoods OR ManuExemptedGoods THEN
                                      MainSeperateAcc := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      MainSeperateAcc := 'N';

                                    IF ProvExemptedGoods THEN
                                      ProvExemptedGoodsText := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      ProvExemptedGoodsText := 'N';

                                    IF ManuExemptedGoods THEN
                                      ManuExemptedGoodsText := 'Y'
                                    ELSE
                                      ManuExemptedGoodsText := 'N';
                                  END;

                                  IF (Service_Provider = '') AND
                                     ((Service_Reciever <> '') OR (CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" OR IPserviceDistributor))
                                  THEN BEGIN
                                    ProvExemptedGoodsText := '';
                                    MainSeperateAcc := '';
                                    ManuExemptedGoodsText := '';
                                  END;

                                  STPayableNotPaid := 0;
                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',STEntryDetail.Type::Sale,STEntryDetail.Type::Charge);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Closed,FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + -STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',STEntryDetail.Type::Sale,STEntryDetail.Type::Charge);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Closed (eCess)",FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + -STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER(Type,'%1|%2',STEntryDetail.Type::Sale,STEntryDetail.Type::Charge);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Closed (SHECess)",FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + -STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Closed Reverse Charge",FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
