                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Closed Reverse Charge (eCESS)",FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                  STEntryDetail.SETCURRENTKEY(Type,"Service Tax Registration No.","Posting Date",Closed);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETFILTER("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                  IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                    STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetail.Type::Purchase);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Reverse Charge",TRUE);
                                  STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Closed Rev. Charge (SHECess)",FALSE);
                                  IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      STPayableNotPaid := STPayableNotPaid + STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                    UNTIL STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0;

                                  //body 2

                                  IF CompInfo."Input Service Distributor" THEN
                                    IfvalueComputed := FALSE
                                  ELSE
                                    IF IPserviceDistributor THEN
                                      IfvalueComputed := FALSE;

                                  IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                    K := 0;
                                    Location.RESET;
                                    Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF Location.FIND('-') OR (CompInfo."Service Tax Registration No." = STN) THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        RG23APartII.RESET;
                                        RG23CPartII.RESET;
                                        IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                        ELSE
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        END;
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                        END;
                                        IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            K := 0;
                                            ECCNo.GET(RG23APartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 1;
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 2;
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 3;
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 4;
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 5;
                                            IF ((RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                                OR (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 6;

                                            IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                              IF NOT RG23APartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                PaymentofExcise[K] += RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."ADE Debit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                                PaymentofExciseCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Debit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                              END;
                                              IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                                 CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                 NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                                CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                CCSTOnInputs[K] += RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                  RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                                CCSTOnInputsCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                              END;
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);

                                        K := 0;
                                        IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                        ELSE
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                        IF RG23CPartII.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            ECCNo.GET(RG23CPartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 1;
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 2;
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 3;
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 4;
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 5;
                                            IF ((RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                                OR (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 6;

                                            IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                              IF NOT RG23CPartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                PaymentofExcise[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPartII."SED Debit" +
                                                  RG23CPartII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                  RG23CPartII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                                PaymentofExciseCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Debit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                              END;
                                              IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer)
                                                 AND CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23CPartII.Type = RG23CPartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                 NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                  CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2;
                                                  CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" ;
                                                  CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" ;
                                                END;
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                  CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                    RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2;
                                                  CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" ;
                                                  CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                                END;
                                              END;
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (RG23CPartII.NEXT = 0);
                                      UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    STasExciseUtilisation.RESET;
                                    STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                    IF STasExciseUtilisation.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) OR
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 1;
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) OR
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 2;
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                            OR (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 3;
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                            OR (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 4;
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                            OR (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 5;
                                        IF ((STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                            OR (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 6;
                                        IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          PaymentofExcise[K] += STasExciseUtilisation."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                          PaymentofExciseCess[K] += STasExciseUtilisation."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation" +
                                            STasExciseUtilisation."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation";
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (STasExciseUtilisation.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",FALSE);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));

                                    IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 1;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 2;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 3;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 4;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 5;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 6;

                                        IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          IF NOT STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge" THEN BEGIN
                                            CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                            CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                          END ELSE
                                            IF STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                              CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                              CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] +=
                                                STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                            END;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",TRUE);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                    IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 1;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 2;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 3;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 4;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 5;
                                        IF ((STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) OR
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 6;
                                        IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          CCSTAsRecFromISD[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                          CCSTAsRecFromISDCess[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    STPaymentDetail1.RESET;
                                    STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                    IF STPaymentDetail1.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 1;
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 2;
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 3;
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 4;
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 5;
                                        IF ((STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) OR
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 6;

                                        IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          PaymentOfST[K] += STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed";
                                          PaymentofSTCess[K] += STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (eCess)" + STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (SHECess)";
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (STPaymentDetail1.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    RASandLTU.RESET;
                                    RASandLTU.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      RASandLTU.SETRANGE(Date,DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      RASandLTU.SETRANGE(Date,DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                    IF RASandLTU.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 1;
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 2;
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 3;
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 4;
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 5;
                                        IF ((RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) OR
                                            (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                        THEN
                                          K := 6;

                                        IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                          CreditUtilizedForRAS[K] += RASandLTU."For Removed as such";
                                          CreditUtilizedForRASCess[K] += RASandLTU."For Removed as such(eCess)" + RASandLTU."For Removed as such(SHE Cess)";
                                          IF NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable" THEN BEGIN
                                            CreditUtilizedForLTU[K] += RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU";
                                            CreditUtilizedForLTUCess[K] += RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU(eCess)" + RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU(SHE Cess)";
                                          END;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (RASandLTU.NEXT = 0);

                                    Location.RESET;
                                    Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF Location.FIND('-') OR (CompInfo."Service Tax Registration No." = STN) THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        RG23APartII.RESET;
                                        RG23CPartII.RESET;
                                        IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                        ELSE
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                        END;
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                          RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        END;
                                        IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            ECCNo.GET(RG23APartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                            IF NOT RG23APartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                              OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] -
                                                (RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."ADE Debit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                              OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] - (RG23APartII."eCess Debit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                            END;
                                            IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                               CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                               NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                (RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit");
                                              OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] + (RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                            END ELSE BEGIN
                                              OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                (RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                 RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit");
                                              OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] + (RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);

                                        IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                        ELSE
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                          RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        IF RG23CPartII.FINDSET THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            ECCNo.GET(RG23CPartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                            IF NOT RG23CPartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                              OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] -
                                                (RG23CPartII."BED Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPartII."SED Debit" +
                                                 RG23CPartII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                 RG23CPartII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                              OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] - (RG23CPartII."eCess Debit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                            END;
                                            IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                               CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23CPartII.Type = RG23CPartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                               NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                            THEN BEGIN
                                              IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2);
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2);
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit") ;
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit") ;
                                              END;
                                            END ELSE BEGIN
                                              IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                   RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2);
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2);
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit") ;
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                  (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                              END;
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (RG23CPartII.NEXT = 0);
                                      UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                    STasExciseUtilisation.RESET;
                                    STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF STasExciseUtilisation.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] - STasExciseUtilisation."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] -
                                          (STasExciseUtilisation."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation" + STasExciseUtilisation."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation");
                                      UNTIL (STasExciseUtilisation.NEXT = 0);

                                    STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",FALSE);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF NOT STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge" THEN BEGIN
                                          OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                          OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                            (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                        END ELSE
                                          IF STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                            OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                            OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                              (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                          END;
                                      UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                    STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                    STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",TRUE);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                          (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                      UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                    K := 0;
                                    STPaymentDetail1.RESET;
                                    STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                    IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                    IF STPaymentDetail1.FIND('-') THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] - STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed";
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] -
                                          (STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (eCess)" + STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (SHECess)");
                                      UNTIL (STPaymentDetail1.NEXT = 0);

                                    FOR K := 1 TO 5 DO BEGIN
                                      OpeningCenvatCredit[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[K] + (CCSTOnInputs[K] + CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] +
                                                                                              CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] + CCSTAsRecFromISD[K] + CreditTakenforLTU[K]) -
                                        (PaymentOfST[K] + PaymentofExcise[K]);
                                      OpeningCenvatCreditCess[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[K] + (CCSTOnInputsCess[K] + CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] +
                                                                                                      CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] +
                                                                                                      CCSTAsRecFromISDCess[K] + CreditTakenforLTUCess[K]) -
                                        (PaymentofSTCess[K] + PaymentofExciseCess[K])
                                    END;
                                  END ELSE  //body 4
                                    IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly) AND IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                      K := 0;
                                      Location.RESET;
                                      Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF Location.FIND('-') OR (CompInfo."Service Tax Registration No." = STN) THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          RG23APartII.RESET;
                                          RG23CPartII.RESET;
                                          IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                          ELSE
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          END;
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                          END;
                                          IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              K := 0;
                                              ECCNo.GET(RG23APartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                              IF (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF (RG23APartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (RG23APartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23APartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                  PaymentofExcise[K] += RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."ADE Debit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                                  PaymentofExciseCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Debit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                                END;
                                                IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                                   CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                   NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                                THEN BEGIN
                                                  CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                                  CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  CCSTOnInputs[K] += RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                    RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit";
                                                  CCSTOnInputsCess[K] += RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                                END;
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL (RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);

                                          K := 0;
                                          IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                          ELSE
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                          IF RG23CPartII.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              ECCNo.GET(RG23CPartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                              IF (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (RG23CPartII."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23CPartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                  PaymentofExcise[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPartII."SED Debit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                    RG23CPartII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Debit";
                                                  PaymentofExciseCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Debit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Debit";
                                                END;
                                                IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                                   CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23CPartII.Type = RG23CPartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                   NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                                THEN BEGIN
                                                  IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                    CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2;
                                                    CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                                    CreditTakenforLTU[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" ;
                                                    CreditTakenforLTUCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" ;
                                                  END;
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                    CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                      RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2;
                                                    CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                                    CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] += RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                      RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" ;
                                                    CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] += RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit";
                                                  END;
                                                END;
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL (RG23CPartII.NEXT = 0);
                                        UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                      K := 0;
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.RESET;
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STasExciseUtilisation.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                             (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 1;
                                          IF (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                             (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 2;
                                          IF (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                             (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 3;
                                          IF (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                             (STasExciseUtilisation."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 4;
                                          IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            PaymentofExcise[K] += STasExciseUtilisation."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                            PaymentofExciseCess[K] += STasExciseUtilisation."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation" +
                                              STasExciseUtilisation."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation";
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STasExciseUtilisation.NEXT = 0);

                                      K := 0;
                                      STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",FALSE);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 1;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 2;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                             (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 3;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                             (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 4;
                                          IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            IF NOT STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge" THEN BEGIN
                                              CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                              CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] +=
                                                STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                            END ELSE
                                              IF STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                                CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                                CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] +=
                                                  STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                              END;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                      K := 0;
                                      STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",TRUE);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 1;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 2;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                             (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 3;
                                          IF (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                             (STEntryDetails."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 4;
                                          IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            CCSTAsRecFromISD[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                            CCSTAsRecFromISDCess[K] += STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                      K := 0;
                                      STPaymentDetail1.RESET;
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF STPaymentDetail1.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 1;
                                          IF (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 2;
                                          IF (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 3;
                                          IF (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                             (STPaymentDetail1."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                          THEN
                                            K := 4;
                                          IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                            PaymentOfST[K] += STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed";
                                            PaymentofSTCess[K] += STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (eCess)" + STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (SHECess)";
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (STPaymentDetail1.NEXT = 0);

                                      K := 0;
                                      RASandLTU.RESET;
                                      RASandLTU.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        RASandLTU.SETRANGE(Date,DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        RASandLTU.SETRANGE(Date,DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                      IF RASandLTU.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 1;
                                          IF (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 2;
                                          IF (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)) THEN
                                            K := 3;
                                          IF (RASandLTU.Date >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND (RASandLTU.Date <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)) THEN
                                            K := 4;
                                          IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
