                                            CreditUtilizedForRAS[K] += RASandLTU."For Removed as such";
                                            CreditUtilizedForRASCess[K] += RASandLTU."For Removed as such(eCess)" + RASandLTU."For Removed as such(SHE Cess)";
                                            IF NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable" THEN BEGIN
                                              CreditUtilizedForLTU[K] += RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU";
                                              CreditUtilizedForLTUCess[K] += RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU(eCess)" + RASandLTU."From ITU for LTU(SHE Cess)";
                                            END;
                                          END;
                                        UNTIL (RASandLTU.NEXT = 0);

                                      Location.RESET;
                                      Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF Location.FIND('-') OR (CompInfo."Service Tax Registration No." = STN) THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          RG23APartII.RESET;
                                          RG23CPartII.RESET;
                                          IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                          ELSE
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                          END;
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                            RG23APartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          END;
                                          IF RG23APartII.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              ECCNo.GET(RG23APartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                              IF NOT RG23APartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] -
                                                  (RG23APartII."BED Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23APartII."SED Debit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."SAED Debit" + RG23APartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23APartII."ADET Debit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."ADE Debit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] - (RG23APartII."eCess Debit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                              END;
                                              IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                                 CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23APartII.Type = RG23APartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                 NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit");
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] + (RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                  (RG23APartII."BED Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(GSI) Credit" + RG23APartII."SED Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."SAED Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23APartII."ADET Credit" + RG23APartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                   RG23APartII."ADE Credit" + RG23APartII."ADC VAT Credit");
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] + (RG23APartII."eCess Credit" + RG23APartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL (RG23APartII.NEXT = 0);

                                          IF Location.Code <> '' THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",Location."E.C.C. No.")
                                          ELSE
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Location E.C.C. No.",CompInfo."E.C.C. No.");
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                            RG23CPartII.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          IF RG23CPartII.FINDSET THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              ECCNo.GET(RG23CPartII."Location E.C.C. No.");
                                              IF NOT RG23CPartII."Excise Credit Availed as ST" THEN BEGIN
                                                OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] -
                                                  (RG23CPartII."BED Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Debit" + RG23CPartII."SED Debit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."SAED Debit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Debit" + RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Debit" +
                                                   RG23CPartII."ADE Debit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Debit");
                                                OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] :=
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] - (RG23CPartII."eCess Debit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Debit");
                                              END;
                                              IF (ECCNo."Type of Unit" = ECCNo."Type of Unit"::Manufacturer) AND
                                                 CompInfo."Large Tax Payer" AND (RG23CPartII.Type = RG23CPartII.Type::Transfer) AND
                                                 NOT CompInfo."Central STC Applicable"
                                              THEN BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                  OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2);
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2);
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit") ;
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit") ;
                                                END;
                                              END ELSE BEGIN
                                                IF NOT RG23CPartII."Deferred Claim" THEN BEGIN
                                                  OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SED Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" / 2 +
                                                     RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit" / 2);
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                    RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" / 2 + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit" / 2;
                                                END ELSE BEGIN
                                                  OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."BED Credit" + RG23CPartII."AED(GSI) Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SED Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."SAED Credit" + RG23CPartII."NCCD Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADET Credit" +
                                                     RG23CPartII."AED(TTA) Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADE Credit" + RG23CPartII."ADC VAT Credit") ;
                                                  OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                    (RG23CPartII."eCess Credit" + RG23CPartII."SHE Cess Credit");
                                                END;
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL (RG23CPartII.NEXT = 0);
                                        UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                      STasExciseUtilisation.RESET;
                                      STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STasExciseUtilisation.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF STasExciseUtilisation.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] - STasExciseUtilisation."ST as Excise Utilisation";
                                          OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] -
                                            (STasExciseUtilisation."ST eCess as Excise Utilisation" + STasExciseUtilisation."ST SHECess Excise Utilisation");
                                        UNTIL (STasExciseUtilisation.NEXT = 0);

                                      STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",FALSE);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          IF NOT STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge" THEN BEGIN
                                            OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                            OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                              (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                          END ELSE
                                            IF STEntryDetails."Reverse Charge Pmt. Doc. No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                              OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                              OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                                (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                            END;
                                        UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                      STEntryDetails.RESET;
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE(Type,STEntryDetails.Type::Purchase);
                                      STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("ST Credit Received",TRUE);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STEntryDetails.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF STEntryDetails.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] + STEntryDetails."Service Tax Amount";
                                          OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] +
                                            (STEntryDetails."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetails."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                        UNTIL (STEntryDetails.NEXT = 0);

                                      STPaymentDetail1.RESET;
                                      STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                        STPaymentDetail1.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                      IF STPaymentDetail1.FIND('-') THEN
                                        REPEAT
                                          OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[1] - STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed";
                                          OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] -
                                            (STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (eCess)" + STPaymentDetail1."Credit availed (SHECess)");
                                        UNTIL (STPaymentDetail1.NEXT = 0);

                                      FOR K := 1 TO 3 DO BEGIN
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatCredit[K] + (CCSTOnInputs[K] + CCSTOnCapitalGoods[K] +
                                                                                                CCSTOnISRecDirectly[K] + CCSTAsRecFromISD[K] + CreditTakenforLTU[K]) -
                                          (PaymentOfST[K] + PaymentofExcise[K]);
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatCreditCess[K] + (CCSTOnInputsCess[K] + CCSTOnCapitalGoodsCess[K] +
                                                                                                        CCSTOnISRecDirectlyCess[K] +
                                                                                                        CCSTAsRecFromISDCess[K] + CreditTakenforLTUCess[K]) -
                                          (PaymentofSTCess[K] + PaymentofExciseCess[K])
                                      END;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[3] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[3] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[4] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[4] := 0;
                                      END;
                                      IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[1] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[1] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCredit[2] := 0;
                                        OpeningCenvatCreditCess[2] := 0;
                                      END;
                                    END ELSE  //body 6
                                      IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Monthly) AND NOT IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                        K := 0;
                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Input Service Distribution",TRUE);
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 1;
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 2;
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 3;
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 4;
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 5;
                                            IF ((STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                                OR (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                            THEN
                                              K := 6;
                                            IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                              CrTakenIPService[K] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                              CrTakenIPServiceCess[K] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                            END;
                                          UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                        K := 0;
                                        Location.RESET;
                                        Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        Location.SETRANGE("Input Service Distributor",TRUE);
                                        IF Location.FIND('-') THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            STDistribution.RESET;
                                            STDistribution.SETRANGE("Svc. Tax Registration. No Rcpt",STN);
                                            STDistribution.SETRANGE("From Location",Location.Code);
                                            IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                            IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));

                                            IF STDistribution.FIND('-') THEN
                                              REPEAT
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,4,Year))
                                                    OR (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,10,Year)))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 1;
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,5,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,5,Year))
                                                    OR (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,11,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,11,Year)))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 2;
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,6,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                                    OR (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,12,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year)))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 3;
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,7,Year)) OR
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,1,Year + 1)))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 4;
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,8,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,8,Year)) OR
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,2,Year + 1)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1) - 1))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 5;
                                                IF ((STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,9,Year)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year)) OR
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,3,Year + 1)) AND
                                                    (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1)))
                                                THEN
                                                  K := 6;
                                                IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                  IF NOT STDistribution."Loaded on Service Account" THEN BEGIN
                                                    CrDistributed[K] += STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                    CrDistributedCess[K] +=
                                                      STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                                    CrNotDistributed[K] += STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                    CrNotDistributedCess[K] +=
                                                      STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                                  END;
                                                END;
                                              UNTIL (STDistribution.NEXT = 0);
                                          UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                        STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Input Service Distribution",TRUE);
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                        IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                        IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] + STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] + STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" +
                                              STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                          UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                        Location.RESET;
                                        Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                        Location.SETRANGE("Input Service Distributor",TRUE);
                                        IF Location.FIND('-') THEN
                                          REPEAT
                                            STDistribution.RESET;
                                            STDistribution.SETRANGE("Svc. Tax Registration. No Rcpt",STN);
                                            STDistribution.SETRANGE("From Location",Location.Code);
                                            IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                            IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                            IF STDistribution.FIND('-') THEN
                                              REPEAT
                                                OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] - STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] - (STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" +
                                                                                                                STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                              UNTIL (STDistribution.NEXT = 0);
                                          UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                        FOR K := 1 TO 5 DO BEGIN
                                          OpeningCenvatIPCredit[K +
                                                                1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[K] + CrTakenIPService[K] - (CrDistributed[K] + CrNotDistributed[K]);
                                          OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[K] + CrTakenIPServiceCess[K] - (CrDistributedCess[K] +
                                                                                                                                        CrNotDistributedCess[K]);
                                        END;
                                      END ELSE //body 8
                                        IF (CompInfo."ST Payment Period" = CompInfo."ST Payment Period"::Quarterly) AND NOT IfvalueComputed THEN BEGIN
                                          K := 0;
                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Input Service Distribution",TRUE);
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                            STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                            STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 1;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 2;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 3;
                                              IF (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                 (STEntryDetail."Posting Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                              THEN
                                                K := 4;
                                              IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                CrTakenIPService[K] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                                CrTakenIPServiceCess[K] += STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                              END;
                                            UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                          K := 0;
                                          Location.RESET;
                                          Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          Location.SETRANGE("Input Service Distributor",TRUE);
                                          IF Location.FIND('-') THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              STDistribution.RESET;
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Svc. Tax Registration. No Rcpt",STN);
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("From Location",Location.Code);
                                              IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                                STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",DMY2DATE(1,4,Year),DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                              IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                                STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",DMY2DATE(1,10,Year),DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1));

                                              IF STDistribution.FIND('-') THEN
                                                REPEAT
                                                  IF (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,4,Year)) AND
                                                     (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,6,Year))
                                                  THEN
                                                    K := 1;
                                                  IF (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,7,Year)) AND
                                                     (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(30,9,Year))
                                                  THEN
                                                    K := 2;
                                                  IF (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,10,Year)) AND
                                                     (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,12,Year))
                                                  THEN
                                                    K := 3;
                                                  IF (STDistribution."Invoice Date" >= DMY2DATE(1,1,Year + 1)) AND
                                                     (STDistribution."Invoice Date" <= DMY2DATE(31,3,Year + 1))
                                                  THEN
                                                    K := 4;
                                                  IF K > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                                    IF NOT STDistribution."Loaded on Service Account" THEN BEGIN
                                                      CrDistributed[K] += STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                      CrDistributedCess[K] +=
                                                        STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                                    END ELSE BEGIN
                                                      CrNotDistributed[K] += STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                      CrNotDistributedCess[K] +=
                                                        STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" + STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                                    END;
                                                  END;
                                                UNTIL (STDistribution.NEXT = 0);
                                            UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                          STEntryDetail.RESET;
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Input Service Distribution",TRUE);
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                            STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                            STEntryDetail.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                          IF STEntryDetail.FINDFIRST THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] + STEntryDetail."Service Tax Amount";
                                              OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] + STEntryDetail."Service Tax eCess Amount" +
                                                STEntryDetail."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount";
                                            UNTIL (STEntryDetail.NEXT = 0);

                                          Location.RESET;
                                          Location.SETRANGE("Service Tax Registration No.",STN);
                                          Location.SETRANGE("Input Service Distributor",TRUE);
                                          IF Location.FIND('-') THEN
                                            REPEAT
                                              STDistribution.RESET;
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("Svc. Tax Registration. No Rcpt",STN);
                                              STDistribution.SETRANGE("From Location",Location.Code);
                                              IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN
                                                STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",0D,DMY2DATE(31,3,Year));
                                              IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN
                                                STDistribution.SETRANGE("Invoice Date",0D,DMY2DATE(30,9,Year));
                                              IF STDistribution.FIND('-') THEN
                                                REPEAT
                                                  OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] - STDistribution."Service Tax Amount";
                                                  OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] - (STDistribution."Service Tax eCess Amount" +
                                                                                                                  STDistribution."Service Tax SHE Cess Amount");
                                                UNTIL (STDistribution.NEXT = 0);
                                            UNTIL (Location.NEXT = 0);

                                          FOR K := 1 TO 3 DO BEGIN
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[K +
                                                                  1] := OpeningCenvatIPCredit[K] + CrTakenIPService[K] - (CrDistributed[K] + CrNotDistributed[K]);
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[K + 1] := OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[K] + CrTakenIPServiceCess[K] - (CrDistributedCess[K] +
                                                                                                                                          CrNotDistributedCess[K]);
                                          END;

                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Apr-Sept" THEN BEGIN
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[3] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[3] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[4] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[4] := 0;
                                          END;
                                          IF MonthRange = MonthRange::"Oct-March" THEN BEGIN
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[1] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[1] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCredit[2] := 0;
                                            OpeningCenvatIPCreditCess[2] := 0;
                                          END;
                                        END;
                                END;
                                 }

               SourceExpr=MainSeperateAcc }

    PROCEDURE GetPaymentDueDate@1500008(PostingDate@1500000 : Date) : Date;
    VAR
      STaxPeriodDueDate@1500001 : Record 16589;
    BEGIN
      STaxPeriodDueDate.RESET;
      STaxPeriodDueDate.SETCURRENTKEY("Starting Date");
      STaxPeriodDueDate.SETFILTER("Starting Date",'<=%1',PostingDate);
      STaxPeriodDueDate.SETFILTER("Ending Date",'>=%1',PostingDate);
      STaxPeriodDueDate.FINDFIRST;
      STaxPeriodDueDate.TESTFIELD("Payment Due Date");
      EXIT(STaxPeriodDueDate."Payment Due Date");
    END;

    PROCEDURE InsertChallanDetail@1500000(EntryNo@1500000 : Integer;ChallanNo@1500002 : Code[20];ChallanDate@1500003 : Date;K@1500001 : Integer);
    BEGIN
      IF ChallanNo = '' THEN
        EXIT;
      IF K = 0 THEN
        EXIT;

      IF K = 1 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp1."Entry No." + 1;
          NoofEntries[1] := NoofEntries[1] + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp1.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
      IF K = 2 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp2."Entry No." + 1;
          NoofEntries[2] := NoofEntries[2] + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp2.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
      IF K = 3 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          NoofEntries[3] := NoofEntries[3] + 1;
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp3."Entry No." + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp3.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
      IF K = 4 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp4."Entry No." + 1;
          NoofEntries[4] := NoofEntries[4] + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp4.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
      IF K = 5 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp5."Entry No." + 1;
          NoofEntries[5] := NoofEntries[5] + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp5.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
      IF K = 6 THEN BEGIN
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.","Challan No.");
        RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.SETRANGE("Challan No.",ChallanNo);
        IF NOT RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          EntryNo := 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.RESET;
          IF RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.FINDLAST THEN
            EntryNo := RecSTEntryDetailTemp6."Entry No." + 1;
          NoofEntries[6] := NoofEntries[6] + 1;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.INIT;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6."Entry No." := EntryNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6."Challan No." := ChallanNo;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6."Challan Date" := ChallanDate;
          RecSTEntryDetailTemp6.INSERT;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
